ical systems is presented. Concepts in data acquisition, feature extraction, data normalization, and statistical modeling will be introduced in an integrated context. Matlab-based exercise. Term project. Use of computer resources. ' ),( 'SE 168' , 'Structural System Testing and Model Correlation
