		  to the Literature of the British Isles: 1832–Present', 'An introduction to the literatures written in English in Britain, Ireland, and the British Empire (and the former British Empire) from 1832 to the present, with a focus on the interaction of text and history. ' ),( 'LTEN 25' , 'Introduction
