Readings in Greek from ancient Greek drama. May be taken for credit four times as topics vary. ' ),( 'LTGK 199' , 'Special Studies', '
Readings in Greek from ancient Greek prose. May be taken for credit four times as topics vary. ' ),( 'LTIT 2A' , 'Intermediate Italian I', '
