				 to build critical and quantitative thinking and research insights and abilities.  ** Consent of instructor to enroll possible  **' ),( 'SIO 102' , 'Introduction to Geochemistry', 'An introduction to the chemical composition and evolution of the Earth and solar system. Applications of chemical methods to elucidate the origin and geologic history of the Earth and the planets, evolution of oceans and atmosphere, and human environmental impacts.  ** Consent of instructor to enroll possible  **' ),( 'SIO 103' , 'Introduction to Geophysics', 'An introduction to the structure and composition
